      "end": 447.01,
      "text": "He jumped into her arms."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.15,
      "end": 455.59,
      "text": "Mrs. Vanderoosie always wanted trouble to go to someone who loved him."
    },
    {
      "start": 455.59,
      "end": 458.85,
      "text": "돌아가신 할머니 이야기를 해주고 있어요."
