    {
      "start": 669.57,
      "end": 669.97,
      "text": "라는 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.73,
      "end": 671.81,
      "text": "아니, 월세도 밀리고."
    },
    {
      "start": 672.49,
      "end": 675.39,
      "text": "뭐 지금 지출이 장난 아닌데."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.65,
      "end": 676.65,
      "text": "She needs the money."
    },
    {
      "start": 676.65,
      "end": 677.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.25,
      "end": 677.73,
      "text": "Take the money."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.73,
      "end": 677.75,
      "text": "Take the money."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.75,
      "end": 678.21,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 678.21,
      "end": 681.79,
      "text": "하지만 뭐, she believes she can deal with it."
    },
    {
      "start": 682.29,
      "end": 682.73,
      "text": "On her own."
    },
    {
      "start": 682.79,
      "end": 683.01,
      "text": "Oh!"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.59,
      "end": 685.43,
      "text": "그렇긴 때문에 이렇게 이야기하지 않았을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.57,
      "end": 686.75,
      "text": "I think so."
    },
    {
      "start": 686.75,
      "end": 686.93,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 687.57,
      "end": 690.73,
      "text": "She thinks she's going to be very successful as a singer."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.85,
      "end": 691.13,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 691.45,
      "end": 695.29,
      "text": "And I think she's just very happy to get the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 695.35,
      "end": 695.67,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 695.79,
      "end": 696.31,
      "text": "The love."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.55,
      "end": 697.95,
      "text": "But 돈도 받아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.27,
      "end": 698.79,
      "text": "돈도 받고."
    },
    {
      "start": 699.03,
      "end": 704.43,
      "text": "아마 이렇게 예쁜 마음을 가졌기 때문에 모든 걸 다 가지게 된 게 아닐까 싶습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 704.55,
      "end": 705.13,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 705.13,
      "end": 706.63,
      "text": "마음 달려있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 706.77,
      "end": 706.95,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 707.35,
      "end": 708.77,
      "text": "자, 마지막으로 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 708.77,
      "end": 711.56,
      "text": "Looks like trouble has made his choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.2,
      "end": 718.48,
      "text": "Mrs. Vanderoosie always wanted trouble to go to someone who loved him and would give him a happy home."
    },
    {
      "start": 719.34,
      "end": 721.52,
      "text": "All that remains is to make it official."
    },
    {
      "start": 722.35,
      "end": 722.59,
      "text": "Wait."
    },
    {
      "start": 723.27,
      "end": 725.03,
      "text": "This means trouble is mine?"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.47,
      "end": 727.71,
      "text": "Not just trouble, but all of it."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.71,
      "end": 730.99,
      "text": "The mansion, the assets, and her fortune."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.47,
      "end": 734.59,
      "text": "But I wouldn't know what to do with all that."
    },
    {
      "start": 734.99,
      "end": 736.03,
      "text": "All I really want is him."
    },
    {
      "start": 736.35,
      "end": 739.07,
      "text": "So, she got it all."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.29,
      "end": 740.53,
      "text": "모든 것을 다 가졌잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 741.33,
      "end": 745.41,
      "text": "그래도 저는 I still wonder how she's going to spend all that money."
    },
    {
      "start": 745.41,
      "end": 749.55,
      "text": "I think she'll use it for something good."
    },
    {
      "start": 749.93,
      "end": 751.67,
      "text": "She doesn't seem like a selfish person."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.25,
      "end": 752.51,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.23,
      "end": 757.83,
      "text": "어떻게 앞으로 이 재산을 쓸지는 내일 알 수 있지 않을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.09,
      "end": 758.63,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.85,
      "end": 759.35,
      "text": "Top secret."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.55,
      "end": 759.73,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.05,
      "end": 762.19,
      "text": "한번 내일 기대해보도록 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 762.41,
      "end": 763.37,
      "text": "Can't wait to find out."
    },
    {
      "start": 763.59,
      "end": 764.57,
      "text": "우리 내일 만나요."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.81,
      "end": 765.37,
      "text": "See you then."
    }
  ]
}